{"body": "Hmm, that doesn't sound good.  I can't reproduce it though - say you have an image_path in your ssl view.  When IE requests the page, `has_request? => true` and `default_protocol => :request`, so we'll use absolute urls with the request's protocol.  Stylesheets will continue referencing protocol-relative urls.  That's what we want, right?", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2777526", "created_at": "2011-11-17T15:49:55Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3660#issuecomment-2777526", "updated_at": "2011-11-17T15:50:39Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 3660, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/jdelStrother", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/a9e5ce6f28587baa2a566eb4f2d76c13?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F269d837afada308dd4aeab28ca2d57e4.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/received_events", "gravatar_id": "a9e5ce6f28587baa2a566eb4f2d76c13", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "jdelStrother", "type": "User", "id": 2377, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jdelStrother/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523833d0bd3543c15100fa8b"}, "id": 2777526, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3660"}
